# Idris Support for the Atom Editor

### Package:

    language-idris

### Getting Information

These key-bindings normally work for the item under the cursor

    Alt-Ctrl-D   Get documentation for the item 
    Alt-Ctrl-T   Display the type


### General

    Alt_Ctrl-R   Reload + type check

### Programming Support for Function Definitions

    Alt-Ctrl-A   Add a definition to a type declaration
    Alt-Ctrl-C   Case Split
    Alt-Ctrl-L   Lift a hole to the top level
    Alt-Ctrl-S   Search
    Alt-Ctrl-M   Match - Replace a hole with a case expression
    